  "archiveofourown": "<div class=\"modal-header\"><button data-dismiss=\"modal\" class=\"close\" type=\"button\">×</button><h3>Archive of Our Own<small class=\"service-url\">Share review <input class=\"share-link\" type=\"text\" value=\"https://tosdr.org/#archiveofourown\" readonly /></small></h3></div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"><div class=\"tosdr-rating\"><label class=\"label false\">No Class Yet</label><p>We haven't sufficiently reviewed the terms yet. Please contribute to our group: <a href=\"get-involved.html\">Get involved</a>.</p></div>\n<section class=\"specificissues\"> <ul class=\"tosdr-points\"><li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11394\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> Users have a reduced time period to take legal action against the service <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11394\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11397\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> Users are responsible for any risks, damages, or losses they may incur by downloading materials <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11397\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11402\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> This service assumes no responsibility and liability for the contents of links to other websites <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11402\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11404\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> You maintain ownership of your data <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11404\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11395\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> The service provider makes no warranty regarding uninterrupted, timely, secure or error-free service <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11395\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11396\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> The services will notify users if personal data has been affected by data breaches <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11396\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11375\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> The service is provided 'as is' and to be used at the users' sole risk <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11375\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11398\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> This service prohibits users sending chain letters, junk mail, spam or any unsolicited messages <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11398\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11399\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> This service is only available to users over a certain age <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11399\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11405\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> Third parties may be involved in operating the service <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11405\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11374\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> Invalidity of any portion of the Terms of Service does not entail invalidity of its remainder <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11374\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11392\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> Failure to enforce any provision of the Terms of Service does not constitute a waiver of such provision <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11392\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-archiveofourown-11373\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> The court of law governing the terms is in location X <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/11373\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></section>\n<section><a href=\"/get-involved.html\" class=\"btn\">Help us find the Terms »</a></section>\n</div>",
