  "phone2action": "<div class=\"modal-header\"><button data-dismiss=\"modal\" class=\"close\" type=\"button\">×</button><h3>Phone2Action<small class=\"service-url\">Share review <input class=\"share-link\" type=\"text\" value=\"https://tosdr.org/#phone2action\" readonly /></small></h3></div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"><div class=\"tosdr-rating\"><label class=\"label false\">No Class Yet</label><p>We haven't sufficiently reviewed the terms yet. Please contribute to our group: <a href=\"get-involved.html\">Get involved</a>.</p></div>\n<section class=\"specificissues\"> <ul class=\"tosdr-points\"><li id=\"popup-point-phone2action-9215\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> This service only shares user information with third parties when given specific consent <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/9215\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-phone2action-9219\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span>  Terms may be changed any time at their discretion, without notice to the user  <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/9219\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-phone2action-9287\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> This service ignores the Do Not Track (DNT) header and tracks users anyway even if they set this header. <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/9287\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-phone2action-9213\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> This service gathers information about you through third parties <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/9213\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-phone2action-9225\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> This service forces users into binding arbitration in the case of disputes <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/9225\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-phone2action-9227\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> This service retains rights to your content even after you stop using your account <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/9227\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-phone2action-9216\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"good\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-success\" title=\"good\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-up icon-white\">+</i></span> Third parties used by the service are bound by confidentiality obligations <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/9216\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-phone2action-9221\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> Users cannot scrape the website of the service <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/9221\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-phone2action-9222\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> Prohibits the posting of pornographic content <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/9222\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-phone2action-9224\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> This service prohibits users sending chain letters, junk mail, spam or any unsolicited messages <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/9224\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-phone2action-9217\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> Your personal data is aggregated into statistics <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/9217\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></section>\n<section><a href=\"/get-involved.html\" class=\"btn\">Help us find the Terms »</a></section>\n</div>",
