  "picturethis": "<div class=\"modal-header\"><button data-dismiss=\"modal\" class=\"close\" type=\"button\">×</button><h3>PictureThis<small class=\"service-url\">Share review <input class=\"share-link\" type=\"text\" value=\"https://tosdr.org/#picturethis\" readonly /></small></h3></div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"><div class=\"tosdr-rating\"><label class=\"label false\">No Class Yet</label><p>We haven't sufficiently reviewed the terms yet. Please contribute to our group: <a href=\"get-involved.html\">Get involved</a>.</p></div>\n<section class=\"specificissues\"> <ul class=\"tosdr-points\"><li id=\"popup-point-picturethis-10617\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"bad\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-warning\" title=\"bad\"><i class=\"icon-thumbs-down icon-white\">-</i></span> This service employs a broad copyright license over user content including the right to distribute through any media <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/10617\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n<li id=\"popup-point-picturethis-10618\" class=\"point\"><div class=\"neutral\"><h5><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\" title=\"neutral\"><i class=\"icon-asterisk icon-white\">⋅</i></span> This service can delete your content if you violate the terms <a href=\"https://edit.tosdr.org/points/10618\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"label context\">Discussion</a></h5><p>Generated through the annotate view</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></section>\n<section><a href=\"/get-involved.html\" class=\"btn\">Help us find the Terms »</a></section>\n</div>",
